SIMPLE: stopcock
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stopcock
<hw>Stop"cock`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A bib,
faucet, or short pipe, fitted with a turning stopper or plug for
permitting or restraining the flow of a liquid or gas; a cock or valve
for checking or regulating the flow of water, gas, etc., through or from
a pipe, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The turning plug, stopper, or spigot of a
faucet.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stope</ent>⟦br⟧
